messages.message:
has anyone had any experience with NetOxygen? https://www.wipro.com/newsroom/press-releases/2019/wipro-gallagher-solutions-launches-netoxygen-los-version-6-0/
We need to help guide our customer on how to integrate into NetO. NetO was the competitor to us - and will be kicked out from an automation perspective but will still be used as an LOS. The customer is saying it's very "costly" to integrate with, but don't fully understand what that means. Any help or guidance would be greatly appreciated
